This directory contains the source files demonstrating performing the summation 
operation using the three different thread libraries: (1) POSIX pthreads, 
(2) Microsoft Win32, and (3) Java.

Compilation instructions for the Pthreads and Java versions are given in the
source files. The Win32 program can be compiled using any Win32 development environment.

Files:

Figure 4.6 - thrd-posix.c

Figure 4.7 - thrd-win32.c

Figure 4.8 - Driver.java


